to teach you

16
00:00:26,909 --> 00:00:29,442
that you don't even know
what you think you know.

17
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,308
Oh, boy.

18
00:00:31,551 --> 00:00:33,684
I'm not going to school.
Why not?

19
00:00:33,769 --> 00:00:35,575
Because I don't know
what's real.

20
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:38,090
Nothing matters.

21
00:00:38,741 --> 00:00:40,200
